text: Franklin County is a county located in the U.S. state of Idaho. As of the 2020 census, 14,194 people lived there. The county seat and largest city is Preston. == Communities == === Cities === * Clifton * Dayton * Franklin * Oxford * Preston * Weston === Unincorporated communities === * Mink Creek * Thatcher * Whitney * Fairview == References == Category:Idaho counties Category:1913 establishments in Idaho
